{"word":"G2517 - καθεξῆς - kathexēs - kath-ex-ace' - After","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καθεξῆς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kathexēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kath-ex-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">After</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஒழுங்காய், பின்பு, வரிசையாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"one after another, successively, in order"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G1836 - ἑξῆς - hexēs - hex-ace'/1836\">G1836</a>; <i>thereafter</i>, that is, <i>consecutively</i>; as a noun (by ellipsis of noun) a <i>subsequent</i> person or time: - after (-ward), by (in) order.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}